---
title: BBQ Cherry-Glazed Haloumi & Slaw with Sweetcorn & Crushed Potato Salad
description: Vegetarians don’t need to miss out on the smokey flavours of the American South with this flavour-packed BBQ and cherry-glazed haloumi, plus all the fixins (including a crunchy slaw)! Enjoy a taste of the good ol’ USA right here.
